%e A327094             +---+
%e A327094 .
%e A327094     +---+---+---+
%e A327094     |         * |
%e A327094 +---+           +---+
%e A327094 |         *   *   * |
%e A327094 +---+---+---+   +---+
%e A327094             | * |
%e A327094             +---+
%e A327094 .
%e A327094     +---+---+---+
%e A327094     |           |
%e A327094 +---+           +---+
%e A327094 | *   *   *   *   * |
%e A327094 +---+---+---+   +---+
%e A327094             |   |
%e A327094             +---+
%e A327094 All other 5-ominoes can fit into this 9-omino too.
%e A327094 From _Peter Exley_, Mar 08 2026: (Start)
